<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Lien invalide</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        background: #f5f7ff;
        color: #2b2f36;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .box {
        width: min(92vw, 520px);
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid rgba(67, 89, 113, 0.14);
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 44px rgba(67, 89, 113, 0.14);
        padding: 28px 24px;
      }
      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 8px;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #566a7f;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <article class="box">
      <h1>Lien invalide ou expire</h1>
      <p>Ce lien de partage n est plus disponible. Demandez un nouveau lien au proprietaire du document.</p>
    </article>
  </body>
</html>
